	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I want to put a custom nes rom, wich is mapper 4 and needs a battery backup, on a TKROM donor board. But this nes rom has vertical mirroring, does TKROM have V or H mirroring or both? Can I change it to fit on TKROM?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

