		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The mirroring is changed by the game via the MMC3, So you have no worries about changing the mirroring on the board via solder pads. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/MMC3#Mirroring_.28.24A000-.24BFFE.2C_even.29">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/MMC3 ... 2C_even.29</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Good luck with this man! ^_^

		

